1
00:02:08,260 --> 00:02:13,340
Eternal Love of Dream

2
00:02:22,020 --> 00:02:23,660
Episode 30

3
00:02:29,460 --> 00:02:32,220
How can I steal the pimpon fruit?

4
00:02:33,540 --> 00:02:34,460
Jiuge.

5
00:02:35,860 --> 00:02:37,580
What are you thinking? You seem so obsessed.

6
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:38,660
Nothing.

7
00:02:39,340 --> 00:02:40,860
Why are you so early, Jielu?

8
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:42,220
Cause I want to get a good seat

9
00:02:42,340 --> 00:02:43,820
where I can be close to the master.

10
00:02:44,060 --> 00:02:46,140
I may fail to get one if I'm late.

11
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:52,380
Jiuge.

12
00:02:52,540 --> 00:02:53,780
Are you here for a seat, too?

13
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:56,860
No, I just woke up early.

14
00:02:57,860 --> 00:03:00,420
I thought you were going to fight over the master with me.

15
00:03:00,820 --> 00:03:02,300
Is there anyone else?

16
00:03:02,660 --> 00:03:03,620
Who else will there be?

17
00:03:03,980 --> 00:03:05,060
Of course the musician.

18
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:06,540
Every time when the master is giving a lesson,

19
00:03:06,740 --> 00:03:08,660
she is always showing her attention nearby.

20
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:10,020
I wonder if Ji Heng still remember

21
00:03:10,020 --> 00:03:11,860
what happened in the mortal world.

22
00:03:13,540 --> 00:03:14,380
Jiuge,

23
00:03:14,940 --> 00:03:16,740
are you listening to me?

24
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:17,860
Yes, I'm listening.

25
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:19,980
The musician came to

26
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:21,700
inseparable king birds in distress over 200 years ago.

27
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:22,980
And the master came here to give lectures

28
00:03:23,140 --> 00:03:24,340
the second year after that.

29
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:26,220
For all these years,

30
00:03:26,380 --> 00:03:27,900
only she has been there to serve him.

31
00:03:28,220 --> 00:03:29,580
Turns out Ji Heng is the reason

32
00:03:29,580 --> 00:03:30,620
why His Majesty is here.

33
00:03:30,980 --> 00:03:32,700
That's typical of him.

34
00:03:33,580 --> 00:03:35,220
The master particularly sets the tea class

35
00:03:35,260 --> 00:03:36,460
in Water Moon Pond,

36
00:03:36,820 --> 00:03:38,460
where the surroundings change from

37
00:03:38,540 --> 00:03:41,220
the season of winter to
what seems to be spring in just a few days.

38
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:42,940
It is so fantastic!

39
00:03:43,660 --> 00:03:45,580
Anything that takes more time and patience,

40
00:03:45,660 --> 00:03:46,540
he's more intrigued.

41
00:03:46,940 --> 00:03:48,860
That's one of his ways of killing time
for he's been living for too long.

42
00:03:51,220 --> 00:03:52,220
The master's here. The master's here.

43
00:03:52,380 --> 00:03:53,100
Come on. Sit.

44
00:03:53,660 --> 00:03:54,380
Sit down.

45
00:04:16,340 --> 00:04:17,820
Yan, come and have a seat.

46
00:04:24,020 --> 00:04:25,500
Xiaojiu, why didn't you call me when you leave?

47
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:26,620
I'm almost late.

48
00:04:26,980 --> 00:04:28,700
You said you didn't want to take the tea class.

49
00:04:28,980 --> 00:04:30,300
But Ji Heng is here.

50
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:34,860
Master,

51
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:38,140
are we drinking Xieyanqing Tea today?

52
00:04:39,180 --> 00:04:41,340
I want to take the liberty of

53
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:44,420
using the tea ware of Rose Green as containers.

54
00:04:46,340 --> 00:04:47,060
Why?

55
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:50,340
Master, I know you often use Black Glaze.

56
00:04:50,940 --> 00:04:51,980
But I think

57
00:04:52,220 --> 00:04:54,340
the color of the celadon

58
00:04:54,540 --> 00:04:55,820
is a great match with that of Xieyanqing Tea,

59
00:04:56,100 --> 00:04:58,060
which conveys a sense of freshness,

60
00:04:58,300 --> 00:05:00,420
and highlights the scenery today.

61
00:05:01,260 --> 00:05:03,220
Why making it so complicated?

62
00:05:04,140 --> 00:05:05,620
I'd go the easy way.

63
00:05:20,020 --> 00:05:20,820
The spirit of drinking tea

64
00:05:21,580 --> 00:05:22,620
lies in the process of making tea.

65
00:05:23,740 --> 00:05:24,740
There are three boiling stages.

66
00:05:25,300 --> 00:05:26,620
Observing and listening are important during the process.

67
00:05:27,540 --> 00:05:29,380
When water boils like fish blowing bubbles
in water with slight sound,

68
00:05:29,780 --> 00:05:30,660
it's the first step of boiling.

69
00:05:31,140 --> 00:05:33,620
When it's like spring gushing over the rim with louder sound,

70
00:05:33,820 --> 00:05:34,860
it comes to the second stage.

71
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:38,020
When it's like sea rolling its waves with intense sound,

72
00:05:38,380 --> 00:05:39,340
it is the third stage.

73
00:05:40,140 --> 00:05:42,620
Ji Heng can stay by His Majesty's side

74
00:05:42,980 --> 00:05:44,740
like the way she did in Tai Chen Palace.

75
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:48,140
While I can only look at them from a distance.

76
00:05:51,540 --> 00:05:52,380
I have explained the method of making tea

77
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:54,660
very clearly.

78
00:05:55,300 --> 00:05:58,500
Now it's your time to get yourselves familiar with it.

79
00:05:59,940 --> 00:06:00,500
Master,

80
00:06:01,060 --> 00:06:02,140
can I make

81
00:06:02,460 --> 00:06:03,860
a proposal?

82
00:06:04,460 --> 00:06:04,980
Sure.

83
00:06:05,780 --> 00:06:08,460
Why don't we have a tea competition?

84
00:06:08,780 --> 00:06:09,980
Master will be the judge,

85
00:06:10,580 --> 00:06:11,860
and the students will compete against one another.

86
00:06:12,900 --> 00:06:14,740
It can be a good way to test

87
00:06:14,940 --> 00:06:16,540
if the students ever listened carefully in class

88
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:20,140
and for them to show what they've learnt.

89
00:06:20,300 --> 00:06:21,540
It works out for everyone.

90
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:25,860
Nice.

91
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:30,900
Yan. Let's make a group.

92
00:06:32,220 --> 00:06:33,900
I thought you've been getting well with Princess Jiuge.

93
00:06:34,100 --> 00:06:35,300
Why don't you choose her?

94
00:06:35,460 --> 00:06:37,020
I know she's not good at tea art,

95
00:06:37,140 --> 00:06:38,660
so I won't go up against her.

96
00:06:39,540 --> 00:06:41,460
Fine, I will lose to anyone anyway.

97
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:52,580
All 15 students have got matched

98
00:06:53,380 --> 00:06:54,820
except Princess Jiuge.

99
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:58,020
Are you willing to be my rival, Princess Jiuge?

100
00:06:58,820 --> 00:06:59,620
It's unfair.

101
00:06:59,900 --> 00:07:01,500
Everyone knows musician is exceptionally skillful in tea art.

102
00:07:01,780 --> 00:07:02,820
Jiuge is a beginner.

103
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:04,300
Musician is too strong for her.

104
00:07:04,980 --> 00:07:06,820
I learn my tea art from master.

105
00:07:07,580 --> 00:07:09,500
Me and Princess Jiuge

106
00:07:09,860 --> 00:07:11,220
are both master's students.

107
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:13,940
Why can't

108
00:07:14,140 --> 00:07:15,420
we compete against each other?

109
00:07:15,860 --> 00:07:16,500
Besides,

110
00:07:16,740 --> 00:07:18,740
Princess Jiuge hasn't said anything yet.

111
00:07:18,980 --> 00:07:20,860
Princess Jielu, why are you so concerned?

112
00:07:21,220 --> 00:07:21,780
Okay.

113
00:07:22,180 --> 00:07:22,980
Let's do this.

114
00:07:23,740 --> 00:07:24,340
I'm not afraid.

115
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:25,140
Great.

116
00:07:25,660 --> 00:07:27,820
Then let's do it first.

117
00:08:52,860 --> 00:08:56,300
The tea made by musician has a delightful aroma,
and it tastes sweet and smooth.

118
00:08:56,580 --> 00:08:58,180
Very good tea making skills.

119
00:09:00,100 --> 00:09:02,620
And the tea made by Princess Jiuge

120
00:09:03,220 --> 00:09:04,260
has a bright color.

121
00:09:04,500 --> 00:09:05,460
It's tasteless at first sip,

122
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:07,900
but the sweet taste lingers on at second sip.

123
00:09:08,140 --> 00:09:09,100
Very unique way.

124
00:09:10,580 --> 00:09:12,540
Both teas have their strong points.

125
00:09:12,780 --> 00:09:14,100
It's too close to call.

126
00:09:20,540 --> 00:09:21,700
Musician said it earlier

127
00:09:22,180 --> 00:09:23,220
that the tea competition

128
00:09:23,660 --> 00:09:26,820
is to test if students listened carefully in class.

129
00:09:27,780 --> 00:09:28,620
Jiuge.

130
00:09:30,300 --> 00:09:32,380
Do you remember

131
00:09:32,620 --> 00:09:34,140
what I said about the first step?

132
00:09:34,660 --> 00:09:36,060
Water first or tea first?

133
00:09:42,260 --> 00:09:43,220
Musician is the winner

134
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:44,780
in this round.

135
00:10:00,100 --> 00:10:00,980
Let's take a break for a quarter of an hour.

136
00:10:01,260 --> 00:10:03,700
Next group. Jielu and Yan Chiwu.

137
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:12,820
Wait.

138
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:16,340
You got something to say to me?

139
00:10:16,740 --> 00:10:18,580
I would take it if I'm less skillful.

140
00:10:18,740 --> 00:10:19,780
But you just decided that I lost

141
00:10:19,980 --> 00:10:20,540
by inventing a reason.

142
00:10:20,740 --> 00:10:21,580
What was that all about?

143
00:10:22,780 --> 00:10:23,740
Have you listened to

144
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:25,420
what I just said?

145
00:10:26,380 --> 00:10:28,420
Just because I didn't listen carefully in your class?

146
00:10:28,620 --> 00:10:29,900
I didn't know that you like holding a grudge.

147
00:10:32,500 --> 00:10:35,700
Clearly you were not listening to me.

148
00:10:36,100 --> 00:10:37,900
Did I have to listen to what you said?

149
00:10:39,420 --> 00:10:40,140
I shouldn't have asked you.

150
00:10:40,300 --> 00:10:40,820
Don't move.

151
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:41,860
What?

152
00:11:01,660 --> 00:11:02,300
You can go now.

153
00:11:15,940 --> 00:11:16,820
Do you know that Ji Heng talked to me today

154
00:11:16,980 --> 00:11:18,460
for quite a few words?

155
00:11:19,500 --> 00:11:21,180
Your group is up. Go.

156
00:11:21,820 --> 00:11:23,300
Yan, don't just sit there and watch.

157
00:11:23,540 --> 00:11:24,380
Get started now.

158
00:11:25,100 --> 00:11:26,700
Alright, time's up.

159
00:11:27,100 --> 00:11:27,580
Yan,

160
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:29,260
your water overflowed.

161
00:11:30,500 --> 00:11:31,180
I think

162
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:33,340
she might have an intention of accepting me.

163
00:11:33,580 --> 00:11:35,780
So she started talking to me over the competition.

164
00:11:40,060 --> 00:11:41,180
I was talking to you.

165
00:11:41,420 --> 00:11:43,220
Your tea has gone cold. Don't drink it.

166
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:48,140
What did he mean?

167
00:11:49,380 --> 00:11:50,260
Xiaojiu.

168
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:51,260
What's wrong with you lately?

169
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:52,780
You have been drifting off.

170
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:55,820
I am talking to you.

171
00:11:56,260 --> 00:11:57,060
What did you say?

172
00:11:57,340 --> 00:11:58,340
I said,

173
00:11:58,540 --> 00:12:00,140
don't care what the ice face said.

174
00:12:00,340 --> 00:12:01,140
I came for you today

175
00:12:01,340 --> 00:12:03,940
because Meng asked us to go drinking in Zuilixian Restaurant.

176
00:12:04,380 --> 00:12:05,460
Go drinking again?

177
00:12:05,620 --> 00:12:06,540
I told you last time.

178
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:08,100
There are some new dancers in Zuilixian Restaurant.

179
00:12:08,220 --> 00:12:09,580
Let's go and have a look.

180
00:12:10,100 --> 00:12:11,340
Okay, let's go.

181
00:12:14,420 --> 00:12:15,740
Why hasn't Jielu come here?

182
00:12:15,900 --> 00:12:17,900
Well, she has been in lock-in for a few days.

183
00:12:18,540 --> 00:12:19,700
Why does she have to go for a lock-in?

184
00:12:19,980 --> 00:12:21,660
It's said that pimpon fruit of this year

185
00:12:21,900 --> 00:12:23,260
can help keep you forever young.

186
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:24,380
So she wants that.

187
00:12:24,940 --> 00:12:27,300
The tournament is about to begin.

188
00:12:27,740 --> 00:12:29,780
But Imperial College does not arrange His Majesty
to give lessons recently.

189
00:12:30,180 --> 00:12:31,780
So she thought she might as well lock herself in to do training.

190
00:12:33,140 --> 00:12:34,300
Well, that explains it.

191
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:35,180
Meng,

192
00:12:35,500 --> 00:12:37,620
these are the new dancers you were talking about?

193
00:12:38,220 --> 00:12:38,900
Yeah.

194
00:12:39,180 --> 00:12:41,140
What do you think? Not bad, huh?

195
00:12:41,940 --> 00:12:44,180
Way worse than Musician Ji Heng.

196
00:12:45,180 --> 00:12:46,940
The tournament is going to begin so soon.

197
00:12:47,460 --> 00:12:48,260
I guess

198
00:12:48,580 --> 00:12:50,020
I have to speed up.

199
00:12:57,460 --> 00:12:59,780
The dancers dance so well and are so good-looking.

200
00:13:00,020 --> 00:13:01,660
Meng, you do have a good eye.

201
00:13:01,900 --> 00:13:03,820
I'll propose a toast to you.

202
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:05,420
Cheers.

203
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:12,420
Fanyin Valley is such a good place.

204
00:13:12,620 --> 00:13:14,740
Beautiful views and beautiful girls.

205
00:13:14,980 --> 00:13:17,300
And the one and only fruiting pimpon tree

206
00:13:17,380 --> 00:13:18,820
in the universe is here.

207
00:13:18,980 --> 00:13:20,660
I thought you wanted to leave here.

208
00:13:20,900 --> 00:13:23,460
Why are you praising it today?

209
00:13:24,940 --> 00:13:27,780
I didn't get used to it when I just got here.

210
00:13:28,020 --> 00:13:29,660
It's lucky for me to have you guys as my friends.

211
00:13:29,900 --> 00:13:30,580
Meng,

212
00:13:30,860 --> 00:13:31,460
cheers.

213
00:13:36,420 --> 00:13:37,260
Meng,

214
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:38,820
cheers.

215
00:13:39,140 --> 00:13:39,860
I'll fill you up.

216
00:13:42,940 --> 00:13:43,820
Cheers.

217
00:13:47,540 --> 00:13:50,620
Speaking of pimpon tree,

218
00:13:50,860 --> 00:13:53,020
I heard the sound of boa constrictors

219
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:54,500
when I passed by Jieyou Spring the other day.

220
00:13:54,740 --> 00:13:56,300
I was so scared that I almost fell to the ground.

221
00:13:56,700 --> 00:13:57,940
I didn't know you could be scared of anything.

222
00:13:58,220 --> 00:13:59,860
I fell into a snake nest by accident

223
00:14:00,020 --> 00:14:01,180
when I was little.

224
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:01,940
Haven't you heard the saying that

225
00:14:02,100 --> 00:14:03,980
a burnt child dreads the fire?

226
00:14:04,660 --> 00:14:06,460
The four boa constrictors are super fierce.

227
00:14:06,660 --> 00:14:07,780
You have to be extremely careful.

228
00:14:07,980 --> 00:14:09,340
Stay away from the snake form.

229
00:14:09,740 --> 00:14:11,060
Will they come out?

230
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:12,100
Don't worry.

231
00:14:12,260 --> 00:14:13,060
They won't.

232
00:14:13,820 --> 00:14:15,540
They are there to protect pimpon tree.

233
00:14:15,740 --> 00:14:16,700
They won't leave easily.

234
00:14:17,420 --> 00:14:18,580
As long as you don't go steal pimpon fruit,

235
00:14:18,820 --> 00:14:19,980
they won't hurt you.

236
00:14:21,300 --> 00:14:23,100
They won't leave easily?

237
00:14:23,420 --> 00:14:24,180
You mean

238
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:25,540
they do leave there at some time?

239
00:14:27,620 --> 00:14:29,100
Meng, let's drink.

240
00:14:29,420 --> 00:14:29,980
Okay.

241
00:14:30,180 --> 00:14:31,180
Cheers.

242
00:14:42,180 --> 00:14:42,740
Top it off.

243
00:14:44,460 --> 00:14:45,620
Let me tell you a secret.

244
00:14:46,660 --> 00:14:47,820
During the full moon,

245
00:14:48,100 --> 00:14:49,020
when Yin Qi reaches its prime,

246
00:14:49,620 --> 00:14:52,060
the four boa constrictors will leave there for a few hours

247
00:14:52,500 --> 00:14:54,180
to absorb spirits of heaven and earth.

248
00:14:59,060 --> 00:15:00,700
Spiritual snakes.

249
00:15:02,060 --> 00:15:02,460
Meng,

250
00:15:02,700 --> 00:15:03,260
drink.

251
00:15:03,660 --> 00:15:04,660
Okay, cheers.

252
00:15:24,980 --> 00:15:25,780
Warrior Yan.

253
00:15:26,180 --> 00:15:28,260
Meng said that during the full moon,

254
00:15:28,500 --> 00:15:30,100
the four boa constrictors will leave, right?

255
00:15:31,180 --> 00:15:32,420
I know you want to steal the fruit.

256
00:15:32,620 --> 00:15:33,020
There are a few hours for you

257
00:15:33,300 --> 00:15:35,260
to try some luck.

258
00:15:38,940 --> 00:15:39,860
Wait a second.

259
00:15:42,780 --> 00:15:44,180
Hello, I want two tomatoes on sticks.

260
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:46,100
You can keep the change.

261
00:15:46,460 --> 00:15:47,180
You...

262
00:15:47,580 --> 00:15:48,420
Okay, you can take as many as you want.

263
00:15:48,580 --> 00:15:49,500
Okay, thank you.

264
00:15:49,540 --> 00:15:50,140
There you go.

265
00:15:52,260 --> 00:15:53,020
Warrior Yan.

266
00:15:53,300 --> 00:15:55,500
Let's go steal pimpon fruit.

267
00:15:56,540 --> 00:15:57,500
No.

268
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:00,780
I heard the pimpon fruit this year

269
00:16:01,020 --> 00:16:03,020
can help you improve your cultivation.

270
00:16:03,580 --> 00:16:04,820
I am good enough.

271
00:16:05,060 --> 00:16:06,780
I don't need pimpon fruit for that.

272
00:16:08,460 --> 00:16:09,540
Take it.

273
00:16:12,460 --> 00:16:14,380
I heard the pimpon fruit this year

274
00:16:14,540 --> 00:16:15,900
can not only improve your cultivation,

275
00:16:16,300 --> 00:16:18,300
but also has the effect of keeping female immortals forever young

276
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:20,660
and making male immortals stronger and more handsome.

277
00:16:23,740 --> 00:16:24,700
Do you think

278
00:16:24,940 --> 00:16:27,060
Ji Heng prefers a strong and handsome man

279
00:16:27,300 --> 00:16:29,380
or a man with porcelain skin like you?

280
00:16:30,660 --> 00:16:31,460
I'll go with you.

281
00:16:32,420 --> 00:16:34,220
Half each when we get the fruit.

282
00:16:34,580 --> 00:16:35,220
Deal.

283
00:16:35,700 --> 00:16:37,780
Just let me know if I can be of any help.

284
00:16:38,220 --> 00:16:39,420
I've already done some research.

285
00:16:39,740 --> 00:16:42,180
Pimpon fruit is in the middle,

286
00:16:42,380 --> 00:16:43,420
