289
00:16:46,460 --> 00:16:49,100
Do you have a better way?

290
00:16:49,740 --> 00:16:51,060
According to Meng,

291
00:16:51,300 --> 00:16:52,020
the four boa constrictors

292
00:16:52,220 --> 00:16:53,780
