293
00:16:54,020 --> 00:16:54,980
We can dig a tunnel

294
00:16:55,180 --> 00:16:56,420
to pimpon tree

295
00:16:56,740 --> 00:16:57,820
and come out

296
00:16:58,100 --> 00:16:59,420
when the four boa constrictors

297
00:16:59,660 --> 00:17:00,700
leave to absorb spirits of heaven and earth.

298
00:17:00,940 --> 00:17:02,900
And then we leave from the tunnel after we get pimpon fruit.

299
00:17:03,220 --> 00:17:04,980
In that way, no one will even know about it.

300
00:17:06,740 --> 00:17:08,420
You are so smart.

301
00:17:09,220 --> 00:17:10,700
Let's go dig the tunnel today

302
00:17:10,700 --> 00:17:12,060
and start to take action tomorrow.

303
00:17:12,820 --> 00:17:13,420
Cool.

304
00:17:22,100 --> 00:17:23,540
Is it done?

305
00:17:23,860 --> 00:17:24,540
Yes.

306
00:17:27,980 --> 00:17:29,460
Do you think we should go down and have a check?

307
00:17:29,740 --> 00:17:31,820
Can the tunnel really connect to pimpon tree?

308
00:17:31,820 --> 00:17:32,620
It's not necessary.

309
00:17:33,020 --> 00:17:35,100
My Locating Magic can't go wrong.

310
00:17:35,380 --> 00:17:35,780
Let's go back.

311
00:17:36,020 --> 00:17:37,260
We'll come here at this time tomorrow.

312
00:17:37,940 --> 00:17:38,940
Wait.

313
00:17:39,980 --> 00:17:41,140
I think you should find something

314
00:17:41,340 --> 00:17:42,220
to cover the hole.

315
00:17:42,580 --> 00:17:43,580
It will be obvious

316
00:17:43,820 --> 00:17:45,460
when the day breaks.

317
00:17:46,460 --> 00:17:47,420
You're right.

318
00:17:53,100 --> 00:17:53,380
Done.

319
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:53,900
Let's go.

320
00:17:54,020 --> 00:17:54,460
Okay.

321
00:18:25,340 --> 00:18:27,020
Master, you're back.

322
00:18:33,820 --> 00:18:34,380
Master,

323
00:18:35,620 --> 00:18:37,580
I've heated the soup for you.

324
00:18:38,100 --> 00:18:38,820
Please drink it while it's hot.

325
00:18:40,060 --> 00:18:41,260
You don't need to

326
00:18:42,260 --> 00:18:43,620
take care of such trivial matters.

327
00:18:44,620 --> 00:18:47,460
Looking after master

328
00:18:47,820 --> 00:18:50,620
is my way of repaying your favors.

329
00:18:53,740 --> 00:18:54,940
It won't consume much of my cultivation

330
00:18:55,340 --> 00:18:56,660
to suppress Qiushui Toxin in you.

331
00:18:57,300 --> 00:18:58,500
You don't have to worry about it.

332
00:18:59,660 --> 00:19:01,620
Master, you have been so good to me.

333
00:19:02,460 --> 00:19:05,300
For my happiness,

334
00:19:05,780 --> 00:19:07,180
you helped me escape the wedding

335
00:19:07,420 --> 00:19:08,620
at the risk of sacrificing your own reputation.

336
00:19:08,980 --> 00:19:12,180
I'm very grateful for all that you've done for me.

337
00:19:13,220 --> 00:19:15,300
As immortals, we have endless time in the world.

338
00:19:15,860 --> 00:19:18,460
Don't be obsessed with things in the past.

339
00:19:19,380 --> 00:19:21,340
But what have happened

340
00:19:21,540 --> 00:19:22,540
is still so vivid to me.

341
00:19:24,980 --> 00:19:27,260
Master, you come to Fanyin Valley once in ten years.

342
00:19:28,060 --> 00:19:29,340
When you are not around,

343
00:19:30,180 --> 00:19:32,380
Fanyin Valley is just

344
00:19:32,660 --> 00:19:35,300
a silent place for cultivation for me,

345
00:19:35,580 --> 00:19:36,740
with no enjoyment at all.

346
00:19:38,580 --> 00:19:40,220
Only when master is around,

347
00:19:41,300 --> 00:19:43,900
can this place be lively again.

348
00:19:45,020 --> 00:19:47,420
I hope master can stay here longer.

349
00:19:48,620 --> 00:19:49,420
So that

350
00:19:49,700 --> 00:19:53,100
I can savor it in the following ten years.

351
00:19:54,220 --> 00:19:54,820
This time,

352
00:19:55,700 --> 00:19:57,700
I will try my best to cure Qiushui Cold Toxin in you.

353
00:19:58,500 --> 00:19:59,980
Since you are not willing to go back to the world of the demons,

354
00:20:00,180 --> 00:20:01,300
you can go

355
00:20:01,980 --> 00:20:03,220
