359
00:20:11,700 --> 00:20:14,460
It was me who insisted on leaving.

360
00:20:14,740 --> 00:20:15,500
Now

361
00:20:16,460 --> 00:20:18,980
I'm too shamed to ask for any title.

362
00:20:19,940 --> 00:20:21,660
All I want is an opportunity

363
00:20:21,940 --> 00:20:23,060
