365
00:20:28,420 --> 00:20:30,260
You don't need to stay by my side.

366
00:20:31,380 --> 00:20:32,460
Is there someone

367
00:20:33,580 --> 00:20:36,820
by your side already?

368
00:20:37,820 --> 00:20:38,580
Or

369
00:20:39,900 --> 00:20:41,700
is there someone on your mind already?

370
00:20:43,740 --> 00:20:44,340
Is it...

371
00:20:45,340 --> 00:20:46,820
Is it Princess Jiuge?

372
00:20:51,180 --> 00:20:51,740
It's late.

373
00:20:52,620 --> 00:20:53,940
Go back and sleep.

374
00:20:55,900 --> 00:20:56,620
Okay.

375
00:21:32,420 --> 00:21:32,940
All right.

376
00:21:33,260 --> 00:21:35,140
I'll go down first since there's no one around.

377
00:21:35,860 --> 00:21:36,420
What's wrong?

378
00:21:36,420 --> 00:21:37,740
I think I should go check first, just in case.

379
00:21:38,020 --> 00:21:38,900
Wait for me.

380
00:21:39,700 --> 00:21:41,060
Be careful.

381
00:22:07,340 --> 00:22:08,500
It's weird.

382
00:22:09,660 --> 00:22:11,660
I remember I only dug one tunnel.

383
00:22:11,860 --> 00:22:13,740
Why are there three sideways?

384
00:22:17,660 --> 00:22:19,260
It's halfway past the time.

385
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:21,620
Why hasn't Yan Chiwu come back?

386
00:22:24,820 --> 00:22:26,940
Does he...

387
00:22:27,780 --> 00:22:29,500
Yan is a good person.

388
00:22:30,260 --> 00:22:31,980
But he used to be a demon lord

389
00:22:32,140 --> 00:22:33,540
who did many evil things.

390
00:22:34,620 --> 00:22:35,700
Is he so damned that he got eaten up

391
00:22:36,660 --> 00:22:38,220
by the boa constrictors?

392
00:22:51,580 --> 00:22:52,780
What the hell is this place?

393
00:22:53,060 --> 00:22:55,780
I'm supposed to come out from under pimpon tree.

394
00:22:56,900 --> 00:22:58,900
Did I dig in the wrong direction?

395
00:23:00,220 --> 00:23:00,980
Never mind.

396
00:23:01,580 --> 00:23:03,500
I'll see if pimpon tree is nearby?

397
00:23:16,420 --> 00:23:17,140
Why...

398
00:23:19,260 --> 00:23:20,620
why did Yan Chiwu dig three tunnels?

399
00:23:20,860 --> 00:23:22,420
We need only one.

400
00:23:24,020 --> 00:23:25,660
It's taking too long for him to check the way.

401
00:23:26,420 --> 00:23:28,420
Could he go the wrong way?

402
00:24:13,220 --> 00:24:15,220
Where on earth is this place?

403
00:24:23,940 --> 00:24:24,540
It's bad.

404
00:24:26,220 --> 00:24:27,460
Sign of a red moon.

405
00:24:27,980 --> 00:24:29,340
Evil spirits are going to come out.

406
00:24:30,260 --> 00:24:31,100
Am I walking into a forbidden area

407
00:24:31,140 --> 00:24:32,660
where evil spirits are bound?

408
00:24:39,700 --> 00:24:43,700
Why don't you even look at me in the eyes, Your Majesty?

409
00:24:44,980 --> 00:24:46,420
Am I not

410
00:24:47,620 --> 00:24:49,380
beautiful enough?

411
00:24:54,740 --> 00:24:55,540
Your Majesty.

412
00:24:56,300 --> 00:24:57,660
You come here only once in ten years.

413
00:24:58,740 --> 00:25:02,380
Do you know how hard and torturing it is

414
00:25:02,820 --> 00:25:04,700
expecting you?

415
00:25:05,900 --> 00:25:06,860
You Majesty.

416
00:25:07,340 --> 00:25:09,460
I'll get mad if you

417
00:25:10,700 --> 00:25:13,140
don't look at me.

418
00:25:13,460 --> 00:25:15,500
Your Majesty, you are dating a banshee here?

419
00:25:16,180 --> 00:25:17,260
What are you doing here?

420
00:25:23,740 --> 00:25:26,100
Your Majesty, you are the most unromantic man

421
00:25:26,380 --> 00:25:27,940
in the Eight Deserts and Six Directions.

422
00:25:28,460 --> 00:25:32,700
Why are you bringing two friends while dating me?

423
00:25:33,460 --> 00:25:36,740
Don't you know that I will be mad?

424
00:25:39,500 --> 00:25:42,700
Oh, His Majesty was talking to her, not me.

425
00:26:07,820 --> 00:26:09,580
Girl, you are so stubborn.

426
00:26:10,420 --> 00:26:12,580
Why don't you leave with your friend?

427
00:26:13,220 --> 00:26:14,220
Do you want to see me

428
00:26:15,060 --> 00:26:17,900
and His Majesty spend the night?

429
00:26:33,100 --> 00:26:33,940
Keep doing what you are doing.

430
00:26:34,260 --> 00:26:35,740
I don't mind watching from aside.

431
00:26:36,780 --> 00:26:38,620
You can tell.

432
00:26:39,380 --> 00:26:41,220
The flowing currents in both of your bodies

433
00:26:41,420 --> 00:26:42,820
are the result of

434
00:26:42,900 --> 00:26:44,180
confrontation between strong spirits.

435
00:26:44,580 --> 00:26:47,180
Foling Flower is the holly flower of Sky Kingdom.

436
00:26:47,820 --> 00:26:49,020
It must be summoned here

437
00:26:49,340 --> 00:26:50,620
by His Majesty

438
00:26:50,820 --> 00:26:52,060
for cleansing his breath.

439
00:26:53,260 --> 00:26:55,660
You seem intimate with each other,

440
00:26:56,300 --> 00:26:58,900
but you are actually having a tough fight in disguise.

441
00:26:59,940 --> 00:27:00,620
Who

442
00:27:00,980 --> 00:27:02,300
are you?

443
00:27:03,020 --> 00:27:04,540
Since you can see it,

444
00:27:05,100 --> 00:27:07,020
you should leave right now.

445
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:12,700
Since you want to be a part of it,

446
00:27:13,020 --> 00:27:15,900
I will give you the satisfaction.

447
00:27:44,100 --> 00:27:45,260
You are just nobody.

448
00:27:45,700 --> 00:27:47,660
How dare you challenge me?

449
00:28:02,940 --> 00:28:05,380
In every move, mind should go earlier than hands.

450
00:28:05,940 --> 00:28:07,100
The sword has to be drawn by the mind.

451
00:28:07,540 --> 00:28:08,900
That's what it takes to win the battle.

452
00:29:26,420 --> 00:29:27,580
Watch closely.

453
00:30:21,780 --> 00:30:23,180
Ji Heng?

454
00:30:26,580 --> 00:30:27,540
Ji Heng.

455
00:30:29,260 --> 00:30:29,820
Why are you here alone

456
00:30:30,060 --> 00:30:31,420
in the middle of the night?

457
00:30:34,980 --> 00:30:35,900
You are crying.

458
00:30:36,620 --> 00:30:37,660
Did the ice face pick on you?

459
00:30:38,100 --> 00:30:38,900
I'll go confront him.

460
00:30:39,580 --> 00:30:40,660
It's none of his business.

461
00:30:41,460 --> 00:30:41,980
I...

462
00:30:43,100 --> 00:30:45,420
I came out for a walk and got lost.

463
00:30:46,260 --> 00:30:50,660
And I happened to see the sad
and beautiful lotus pool under moonlight.

464
00:30:51,020 --> 00:30:52,940
So I couldn't help being sentimental here.

465
00:30:53,940 --> 00:30:54,660
No wonder.

466
00:30:55,260 --> 00:30:56,300
Are you lost, too?

467
00:30:56,420 --> 00:30:57,740
I got lost too.

468
00:30:58,020 --> 00:30:59,900
Fanyin Valley is such a weird place.

469
00:31:01,500 --> 00:31:04,340
Let me escort you back.

470
00:31:06,780 --> 00:31:08,020
Thank you, Yan.

471
00:31:10,260 --> 00:31:11,340
What did you call me?

472
00:31:12,940 --> 00:31:14,100
Demon Lord

473
00:31:15,780 --> 00:31:16,580
Yan.

474
00:31:16,860 --> 00:31:18,340
No, no, no. Don't add Demon Lord.

475
00:31:18,460 --> 00:31:20,060
Just call me Yan. It sounds friendlier.

476
00:31:20,580 --> 00:31:22,940
I like you calling me Yan.

477
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:33,020
It's over?

478
00:31:33,380 --> 00:31:34,060
Yes, it's over.

479
00:31:36,500 --> 00:31:37,340
Why are you here?

480
00:31:38,420 --> 00:31:40,060
Who's the banshee?

481
00:31:41,740 --> 00:31:42,380
Wait.

482
00:31:43,140 --> 00:31:45,180
You asked me why I was here?

483
00:31:47,380 --> 00:31:49,580
Did I sound like I was talking to myself?

484
00:31:50,780 --> 00:31:51,460
No.

485
00:31:51,660 --> 00:31:53,500
I thought you asked Ji Heng why she was here.

486
00:31:53,900 --> 00:31:55,380
So you were actually asking me.

487
00:31:56,940 --> 00:31:57,780
Of course.

488
00:32:04,420 --> 00:32:05,460
You haven't answered me yet.

489
00:32:06,540 --> 00:32:07,460
Why are you here?

490
00:32:08,180 --> 00:32:09,140
I...

491
00:32:09,700 --> 00:32:11,180
I'm supposed to be

492
00:32:11,180 --> 00:32:12,260
stealing pimpon fruit at this time.

493
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:13,660
But impulsion ran over me.

494
00:32:13,940 --> 00:32:14,820
And the moment I drew pottery-made sword,

495
00:32:15,020 --> 00:32:17,100
I completely forgot what I was supposed to do.

496
00:32:17,420 --> 00:32:18,980
And I have no idea how much time is left for me.

497
00:32:19,740 --> 00:32:21,340
I've got things to do. I have to go now.

498
00:32:21,620 --> 00:32:23,220
Aren't you going to take me with you?

499
00:32:24,860 --> 00:32:25,780
Why would I do that?

500
00:32:26,620 --> 00:32:27,380
I'm hurt.

501
00:32:28,860 --> 00:32:30,460
Do you want to leave me here alone?

502
00:32:31,340 --> 00:32:32,140
Don't you think it's unsafe for me?

503
00:32:33,180 --> 00:32:33,940
No.

504
00:32:34,220 --> 00:32:35,180
Not at all.

505
00:32:41,580 --> 00:32:42,100
You...

506
00:32:42,700 --> 00:32:44,940
Looks like you don't feel safe leaving me here.

507
00:32:47,380 --> 00:32:48,660
I'm sorry that

508
00:32:48,900 --> 00:32:49,820
I fail to tell

509
00:32:50,020 --> 00:32:51,460
you're hurt,

510
00:32:51,660 --> 00:32:53,140
judging from your charming bearing now.

511
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:05,100
Legend has it that since Your Majesty

512
00:33:05,140 --> 00:33:06,860
took the throne,

513
00:33:07,180 --> 00:33:09,100
