514
00:33:10,300 --> 00:33:12,700
How surprising it is to see you

515
00:33:12,700 --> 00:33:14,820
get hurt today.

516
00:33:16,100 --> 00:33:17,100
Have you had enough?

517
00:33:19,540 --> 00:33:21,340
The red blood is even mixed with goldenness.

518
00:33:22,180 --> 00:33:23,940
Your Majesty's blood is indeed different.

519
00:33:24,340 --> 00:33:25,580
I also heard that

520
00:33:25,780 --> 00:33:27,740
a cup of Your Majesty's blood,

521
00:33:28,100 --> 00:33:30,580
