526
00:33:44,140 --> 00:33:46,060
You have fooled me several times.

527
00:33:46,260 --> 00:33:47,860
Who knows if this is your camouflage trick or not?

528
00:33:48,060 --> 00:33:49,580
I'm no fool.

529
00:33:52,460 --> 00:33:55,700
You are a lot smarter than before.

530
00:33:56,260 --> 00:33:58,100
But didn't your master who taught you magic art

531
00:33:58,260 --> 00:34:00,220
tell you in your childhood that

532
00:34:00,740 --> 00:34:03,140
the camouflage with bleeding can only deceit a mortal,

533
00:34:03,540 --> 00:34:05,660
but not an immortal?

534
00:34:11,180 --> 00:34:12,700
The wound is real?

535
00:34:16,260 --> 00:34:16,860
But

536
00:34:17,660 --> 00:34:19,940
you are not like all the heroes I have met.

537
00:34:20,100 --> 00:34:21,220
Take my uncle for example.

538
00:34:21,860 --> 00:34:23,140
No matter how badly injured he was,

539
00:34:23,420 --> 00:34:24,500
he would try everything he could think of

540
00:34:24,660 --> 00:34:25,980
