541
00:34:26,380 --> 00:34:27,700
It's the first time I saw

542
00:34:27,740 --> 00:34:29,020
someone who had such an overreaction.

543
00:34:31,180 --> 00:34:34,140
Because I am weaker

544
00:34:34,700 --> 00:34:35,820
than those heroes you know.

545
00:34:39,260 --> 00:34:40,940
Am I exaggerating?

546
00:34:42,420 --> 00:34:43,100
Sorry.

547
00:35:25,100 --> 00:35:25,780
Thank you

548
00:35:26,100 --> 00:35:26,980
for escorting me back.

549
00:35:40,420 --> 00:35:41,260
I got lucky

550
00:35:41,500 --> 00:35:42,980
to run into Ji Heng while I was lost.

551
00:35:44,740 --> 00:35:45,180
Oh no.

552
00:35:45,380 --> 00:35:46,340
I forgot about Xiaojiu.

553
00:35:51,260 --> 00:35:51,940
What are you looking at?

554
00:35:53,180 --> 00:35:54,020
I'm thinking.

555
00:35:55,660 --> 00:35:56,340
Thinking about what?

556
00:35:57,460 --> 00:35:58,180
Thinking about you.

557
00:36:06,260 --> 00:36:08,860
Why did you come all the way to Jieyou Spring
in the middle of the night?

558
00:36:09,180 --> 00:36:10,660
Damn, I totally forgot it.

559
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:11,820
Yan...

560
00:36:12,140 --> 00:36:12,860
I...

