00:36:13,380 --> 00:36:14,020
Oh,

562
00:36:14,500 --> 00:36:16,100
I've got something to do. Bye now.

563
00:36:16,900 --> 00:36:17,820
Leaving so soon?

564
00:36:18,780 --> 00:36:20,900
Is that your way of doing things in Qingqiu?

565
00:36:22,100 --> 00:36:23,260
Of course.

566
00:36:23,540 --> 00:36:25,100
I have my own business.

567
00:36:25,540 --> 00:36:27,300
And I've patched you up.

568
00:36:27,540 --> 00:36:29,260
Excuse me if there's nothing else.

569
00:36:34,260 --> 00:36:35,460
I forgot to tell you that

570
00:36:35,860 --> 00:36:37,700
Miao Luo's breaking in will trigger the shut-down,

571
00:36:38,020 --> 00:36:39,300
so she will be trapped here.

572
00:36:39,900 --> 00:36:40,980
Although she's put down,

573
00:36:41,340 --> 00:36:43,100
the shut-down won't go away

574
00:36:43,340 --> 00:36:44,260
until 24 hours later

575
00:36:44,580 --> 00:36:46,020
for making sure nothing goes wrong.

576
00:36:46,380 --> 00:36:47,100
I'm afraid

577
00:36:47,500 --> 00:36:49,020
you can't go out for now.

578
00:36:49,980 --> 00:36:51,660
24 hours.

579
00:36:53,620 --> 00:36:55,100
What's so urgent

580
00:36:56,340 --> 00:36:57,860
that you have to go out now?

581
00:36:58,580 --> 00:36:59,460
I have...

582
00:37:00,660 --> 00:37:02,380
I have an appointment with Yan Chiwu.

583
00:37:03,820 --> 00:37:05,300
Stealing pimpon fruit

584
00:37:05,380 --> 00:37:06,260
is not something I can talk about proudly

585
00:37:06,460 --> 00:37:07,820
with others.

586
00:37:09,700 --> 00:37:12,060
I have an appointment with Yan.

587
00:37:16,340 --> 00:37:16,820
Your Majesty,

588
00:37:17,180 --> 00:37:18,860
do you think

589
00:37:19,060 --> 00:37:19,940
I patched you up well?

590
00:37:20,500 --> 00:37:21,780
Do you owe me once?

591
00:37:22,060 --> 00:37:23,260
Do you want to return the favor?

592
00:37:24,580 --> 00:37:25,420
It's just so-so.

593
00:37:26,500 --> 00:37:28,060
What do you want from me in return?

594
00:37:29,300 --> 00:37:30,180
It's very simple.

595
00:37:30,460 --> 00:37:31,820
Such a place

596
00:37:32,100 --> 00:37:33,860
can only trap low-level immortals

597
00:37:33,860 --> 00:37:35,460
like me.

598
00:37:35,900 --> 00:37:37,140
Those immortals with high cultivation

599
00:37:37,300 --> 00:37:39,060
like you

600
00:37:39,260 --> 00:37:40,700
can't be trapped.

601
00:37:41,060 --> 00:37:41,980
If Your Majesty

602
00:37:42,100 --> 00:37:45,180
can help me get out of here,

603
00:37:45,660 --> 00:37:48,540
I will forgive you for

604
00:37:48,620 --> 00:37:50,380
your not coming to rescue me for over half a year

605
00:37:50,700 --> 00:37:51,820
after leaving me in Fanyin Valley

606
00:37:51,900 --> 00:37:53,980
and your turning into a handkerchief

607
00:37:54,380 --> 00:37:55,380
to deceive me into forgiving you.

608
00:37:55,660 --> 00:37:56,460
What do you think?

609
00:37:56,900 --> 00:37:57,980
I think

610
00:38:04,620 --> 00:38:06,620
you are holding a grudge against me.

611
00:38:07,820 --> 00:38:09,340
I'm not.

612
00:38:10,660 --> 00:38:11,300
Of course,

613
00:38:11,900 --> 00:38:14,420
no one will offend me except you.

614
00:38:17,140 --> 00:38:17,900
What about Yan Chiwu?

615
00:38:18,500 --> 00:38:19,460
Yan.

616
00:38:20,020 --> 00:38:21,180
Well, he's very nice.

617
00:38:28,500 --> 00:38:29,540
So, Your Majesty,

618
00:38:29,900 --> 00:38:32,020
are you going to help me get out

619
00:38:32,220 --> 00:38:33,300
or not?

620
00:38:35,340 --> 00:38:37,220
Why would I help you get out?

621
00:38:38,020 --> 00:38:39,020
Because I helped you.

622
00:38:40,740 --> 00:38:42,580
I helped you at a crucial time.

623
00:38:42,780 --> 00:38:44,380
And you should help me once too.

624
00:38:44,620 --> 00:38:45,740
That's what we call fairness.

625
00:38:46,780 --> 00:38:48,740
I don't know how to get you out.

626
00:38:50,940 --> 00:38:52,700
No matter how important your appointment is,

627
00:38:52,940 --> 00:38:55,220
you have to wait until 24 hours later.

628
00:38:59,140 --> 00:39:00,100
Xiaojiu.

629
00:39:00,940 --> 00:39:02,100
Xiaojiu.

630
00:39:03,820 --> 00:39:04,660
Where is she?

631
00:39:09,300 --> 00:39:10,500
If I miss the chance tonight,

632
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:13,060
I have to wait until the 15th of next lunar month.

633
00:39:13,140 --> 00:39:14,620
It's one more month to go.

634
00:39:18,140 --> 00:39:20,300
I dragged Yan into this.

635
00:39:20,700 --> 00:39:22,140
Now he couldn't find me.

636
00:39:22,220 --> 00:39:23,620
He must be very anxious.

637
00:39:29,460 --> 00:39:32,940
I didn't know that you are so worried about Yan.

638
00:39:33,140 --> 00:39:34,860
I'm afraid he won't help me steal pimpon fruit again

639
00:39:35,060 --> 00:39:37,580
next month.

640
00:39:41,500 --> 00:39:42,380
No.

641
00:39:43,060 --> 00:39:43,900
Nothing.

642
00:39:45,580 --> 00:39:46,820
So you planned to steal pimpon fruit

643
00:39:47,020 --> 00:39:49,460
with Yan Chiwu.

644
00:39:51,180 --> 00:39:52,060
No.

645
00:39:52,980 --> 00:39:54,060
I am the princess of Qingqiu.

646
00:39:54,340 --> 00:39:55,940
I won't do such a thing.

647
00:39:56,100 --> 00:39:57,300
No, you heard it wrong.

648
00:40:00,140 --> 00:40:01,660
Maybe I did hear it wrong.

649
00:40:05,620 --> 00:40:07,140
I'm feeling a bit dizzy.

650
00:40:07,860 --> 00:40:08,620
Come here.

651
00:40:09,700 --> 00:40:10,700
Lend me your shoulder.

652
00:40:12,020 --> 00:40:12,660
Your Majesty.

653
00:40:13,500 --> 00:40:15,220
You may feel uncomfortable leaning on me.

654
00:40:15,620 --> 00:40:17,220
I can conjure a pillow for you.

655
00:40:17,540 --> 00:40:19,540
I feel like I recall something.

656
00:40:20,020 --> 00:40:21,500
You said the 15th of next lunar month...

657
00:40:22,180 --> 00:40:22,700
Your Majesty,

658
00:40:22,900 --> 00:40:24,380
are you feeling comfortable now?

659
00:40:24,620 --> 00:40:27,380
I can lie down for you to lean on.

660
00:40:27,620 --> 00:40:29,700
Should I lie down with my face up

661
00:40:29,820 --> 00:40:31,860
or my back up?

662
00:40:32,660 --> 00:40:35,820
Do you feel better sitting or lying?

663
00:40:36,220 --> 00:40:36,740
If I lie down,

664
00:40:36,900 --> 00:40:38,060
it means both of us are lying.

665
00:40:38,860 --> 00:40:39,860
I think sitting is better.

666
00:40:41,340 --> 00:40:42,620
Okay.

667
00:40:51,060 --> 00:40:51,580
Xiaojiu.

668
00:40:54,900 --> 00:40:55,380
Xiaojiu.

669
00:41:02,700 --> 00:41:04,060
I lost too much blood earlier.

670
00:41:04,540 --> 00:41:05,580
My hands are cold.

671
00:41:05,820 --> 00:41:07,180
Do you mind

672
00:41:08,260 --> 00:41:09,900
warming me up a little?

673
00:41:11,100 --> 00:41:12,340
It's improper for men and women to have physical contact.

674
00:41:14,940 --> 00:41:15,700
Sure.

675
00:41:17,140 --> 00:41:17,660
I want to meet the empress of inseparable king birds

676
00:41:17,900 --> 00:41:20,220
in a few days.

677
00:41:20,540 --> 00:41:22,780
I'll ask her how to plant pimpon tree.

678
00:41:23,020 --> 00:41:24,460
Do you think I should...

679
00:41:24,820 --> 00:41:25,420
Well, I don't think

680
00:41:25,740 --> 00:41:27,180
it's improper for men and women to have physical contact.

681
00:41:27,380 --> 00:41:28,540
That's the most ridiculous thing

682
00:41:28,780 --> 00:41:29,780
moralists come up with

683
00:41:29,980 --> 00:41:30,900
since the creation of the universe.

684
00:41:31,340 --> 00:41:32,620
I'm not sure if my hands are warm enough

685
00:41:33,020 --> 00:41:34,700
for you, Your Majesty.

686
00:41:36,700 --> 00:41:37,620
Quick learner.

687
00:41:38,220 --> 00:41:39,100
I'm tired.

688
00:41:39,420 --> 00:41:40,700
I want to get some sleep.

689
00:41:41,220 --> 00:41:42,300
Suit yourself.

690
00:41:45,100 --> 00:41:45,900
You just stood there

691
00:41:46,020 --> 00:41:47,460
and watched the whole thing.

692
00:41:48,100 --> 00:41:49,820
You're so cheeky to say you're tired.

693
00:41:50,300 --> 00:41:52,740
I just fought a tough fight and I even have to serve you.

694
00:41:52,980 --> 00:41:54,180
I'm much more tired than you.

695
00:41:54,620 --> 00:41:56,860
I know what's in your head.

696
00:41:57,060 --> 00:41:58,580
You think all I did was standing there and watching.

697
00:42:00,620 --> 00:42:02,100
I was encouraging you

698
00:42:03,340 --> 00:42:05,020
very seriously.

699
00:42:07,220 --> 00:42:08,340
I will take you out

700
00:42:08,740 --> 00:42:09,940
after I have enough rest.

701
00:42:57,860 --> 00:42:59,220
I went this way earlier.

702
00:43:00,300 --> 00:43:01,820
Xiaojiu must have gone either of the two ways.

703
00:43:02,340 --> 00:43:03,740
What if she went alone to steal pimpon fruit

704
00:43:03,820 --> 00:43:05,580
and got eaten up by the four boa constrictors?

705
00:43:06,660 --> 00:43:07,620
I have to find her soon.

706
00:43:29,540 --> 00:43:32,820
There are always people out there
trying to seek protection from me.

707
00:43:33,940 --> 00:43:36,980
It's the first time I met someone

708
00:43:37,740 --> 00:43:40,620
who wants to protect me instead.

